<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٣٦ -<span class="c5"> أَنْشَدَنَا أَبُو سَعْدٍ عَبْدُ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنُ مُحَمَّدٍ الْكَاتِبُ لِنَفْسِهِ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[البحر الكامل]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗١٣١⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَا تَعْجَبَنَّ إِذَا اشْتَكَى الْحُرُّ ... الْكَرِيمُ إِلَيْكَ دَهْرَهُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَالْوَقْتُ وَقْتُهُ وَالزَّمَانُ ... زَمَانُهُ وَالدَّهْرُ دَهْرُهُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>